To configure:

adjust first line of Makefile as necessary

  OPTS=-DBANK_C -DWALLET_C -DPADDING=\"4\"

To use:

  Usage: dollar [-b|-w|-i] [amount]

-b: bank
example:
$ dollar -b 100
  Bank:   $ 100

-w: wallet
example:
$ dollar -w 100
  Wallet: $ 100

-i: init
example:
$ dollar -i
Dollar{
  Bank:   $0 000
  Wallet: $  000
}
